column16: Ryan Zimmerman flies out to center fielder Juan Lagares.
Denard Span doubles (1) on a line drive to left fielder Eric Young Jr.   Ian Desmond scores.    Danny Espinosa to 3rd.
Danny Espinosa walks.   Ian Desmond to 2nd.
Anthony Rendon called out on strikes.
Adam LaRoche pops out to third baseman David Wright.
Ian Desmond singles on a ground ball to center fielder Juan Lagares.
